<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
<p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> 01 December 2025</p>

<p>Welcome to <strong>Shri Shorthand (Jain Lipi)</strong>.  
This Privacy Policy explains how our application (“App”, “we”, “our”, “us”) handles user information.</p>

<p>By using the App, you consent to this Privacy Policy.</p>

<hr>

<h2>1. Information We Do Not Collect</h2>
<p><strong>Shri Shorthand (Jain Lipi)</strong> does <strong>NOT</strong> collect, store, or share any personal information from users.</p>

<ul>
    <li>No name, phone number, or email</li>
    <li>No account creation or login required</li>
    <li>No contacts or messages</li>
    <li>No precise location</li>
    <li>No camera photos or personal files</li>
</ul>

<p>The app requires internet to load content.</p>

<hr>

<h2>2. Third-Party Services – Google AdMob</h2>
<p>Our app uses <strong>Google AdMob</strong> to show Banner Ads, Interstitial Ads, and Rewarded Ads.</p>

<p>AdMob may automatically collect certain data for ad delivery and measurement.  
This data is collected by Google and <strong>not</strong> by us.</p>

<h3>Data that Google AdMob may collect:</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Advertising ID (AAID)</li>
    <li>IP address (approximate location, not GPS)</li>
    <li>Device information (model, OS version, hardware)</li>
    <li>App usage interactions (ad views, clicks)</li>
    <li>Crash information</li>
</ul>

<p>Google may use cookies or similar technologies to serve personalized or non-personalized ads based on your region.</p>

<p>Learn more at:  
<a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank">Google Privacy Policy</a></p>

<hr>

<h2>3. Types of Ads Used</h2>
<p>Our app displays the following ad formats through Google AdMob:</p>

<ul>
    <li><strong>Banner Ads</strong></li>
    <li><strong>Interstitial Ads</strong></li>
    <li><strong>Rewarded Ads</strong> (User can watch the ad to unlock content)</li>
</ul>

<p>Ads help support the development and free availability of the application.</p>

<hr>

<h2>4. Permissions Used by the App</h2>

<p>Shri Shorthand (Jain Lipi) uses a few basic permissions only for core app functionality:</p>

<ul>
    <li><strong>INTERNET</strong> – to load ads and online content</li>
    <li><strong>ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE</strong> – to check network status</li>
    <li><strong>READ/WRITE STORAGE</strong> – only to access or save media files used within the app</li>
    <li><strong>AUDIO/VIDEO</strong> – used only for audio or video playback (not recorded or uploaded)</li>
</ul>

<p>We do <strong>NOT</strong> collect or upload any audio, video, or storage data.</p>

<hr>

<h2>5. Children's Privacy</h2>
<p>We do not knowingly collect personal data from children under 13.  
If you believe your child provided data through third-party ads, please contact us immediately.</p>

<hr>

<h2>6. Data Security</h2>
<p>We do not collect any user data, therefore no information is stored on our servers.  
All advertising data is processed securely by Google AdMob.</p>

<hr>

<h2>7. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
<p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time.  
Any changes will be posted here with an updated “Last Updated” date.</p>

<hr>

<h2>8. Contact Us</h2>
<p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, feel free to contact us at:</p>

<p><strong>Email:</strong> shreeeducationclasses@gmail.com</p>

